            <div type="transcript" id="SH14-96">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>"Remember me," implored the Thief --</l>
                    <l>Oh magnanimity!</l>
                    <l>"My Visitor in Paradise</l>
                    <l>I give thee Guaranty."</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>That courtesy will fair remain,</l>
                    <l>When the delight is dust,</l>
                    <l>With which we cite this mightiest case</l>
                    <l>Of compensated Trust.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Of All, we are allowed to hope,</l>
                    <l>But Affidavit stands</l>
                    <l>That this was due, where some, we fear,</l>
                    <l>Are unexpected friends.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
        </body>
